OL,3,CMan posted 'horrific' monkey torture
OL,4,Cvideos on Facebook
OL,6,FA man who posted "horrific" and
OL,7,F"disturbing" videos of baby monkeys
OL,8,Fbeing tortured on Facebook has been
OL,9,Fjailed for 20 months.
OL,11,FPeter Stanley posted three videos
OL,12,Fshowing the torture of long-tailed
OL,13,Fmacaques on a private site, since shut
OL,14,Fdown, linked to the intentional harm
OL,15,Fof animals for entertainment.
OL,17,FThe 43-year-old posted videos along
OL,18,Fwith comments, including: "A fave of
OL,19,Fmine this one."
