OL,6,FBut the videos were spotted by an
OL,7,Fanimal welfare group and the Facebook
OL,8,Fuser ID was given to police who traced
OL,9,FStanley and raided his home.
OL,11,FDetectives seized a mobile phone
OL,12,Frevealing 75 videos of monkeys being
OL,13,Ftortured.
OL,15,FStanley was also found to have been
OL,16,Fsearching terms on the internet such
OL,17,Fas: "How to tell if a baby monkey is
OL,18,Fdistressed" and "Horse Porn".
