OL,3,CMan posted 'horrific' monkey torture
OL,4,Cvideos on Facebook
OL,6,FAfter his arrest, he told police he
OL,7,Fhad become aware of these videos and
OL,8,Fwanted to know just how bad they were
OL,9,Fso joined a Facebook group.
OL,11,FIn order to join, members had to post
OL,12,Fthree videos to show they would not
OL,13,Freport the group to authorities. He
OL,14,Fdid not himself make the videos or
OL,15,Fharm animals directly.
OL,17,FStanley, of Dovecote Avenue, Dovecote,
OL,18,FLiverpool, admitted three counts of
OL,19,Fpublishing obscene material, before he
OL,20,Fwas jailed for 20 months at Liverpool
OL,21,FCrown Court.
