OL,3,CMan posted 'horrific' monkey torture
OL,4,Cvideos on Facebook
OL,6,FHis arrest came after the broadcast of
OL,7,Fa BBC TV documentary, The Monkey
OL,8,FHaters, which uncovered the existence
OL,9,Fof streaming videos containing the
OL,10,Ftorture of baby monkeys.
OL,12,FVideos, primarily filmed in South East
OL,13,FAsia, showed the "disciplining" and
OL,14,Ftormenting of captive infant monkeys
OL,15,Fand the deliberate infliction of pain
OL,16,Fand fear, causing physical harm as
OL,17,Fwell as emotional distress.
