OL,3,CMan posted 'horrific' monkey torture
OL,4,Cvideos on Facebook
OL,6,FThomas Quirk, senior crown prosecutor
OL,7,Fof the Crown Prosecution Service,
OL,8,Fdescribed the videos posted by Stanley
OL,9,Fas "truly horrific".
OL,11,FHe added: "The torture imposed on
OL,12,Fthese animals included sexual torture
OL,13,Fand it has been a distressing case for
OL,14,Fboth the police and the prosecution
OL,15,Fteam to deal with."
OL,17,FSarah Kite, co-founder of Action for
OL,18,FPrimates, hopes the prosecution of
OL,19,FStanley is a "wake-up call" to social
OL,20,Fmedia companies.
