OL,3,CMan posted 'horrific' monkey torture
OL,4,Cvideos on Facebook
OL,6,FShe said: "Those individuals involved
OL,7,Fin distributing graphic and obscene
OL,8,Fcontent depicting the violent and
OL,9,Fsadistic torture and killing of baby
OL,10,Fmonkeys need to know that their
OL,11,Fbehaviour is not only vile, but is
OL,12,Falso a crime.
OL,14,F"We also hope that this prosecution
OL,15,Fwill be a wake-up call to Meta and
OL,16,Fother social media companies that
OL,17,Fcontinue to allow this highly
OL,18,Fdisturbing and graphic content to be
OL,19,Fposted on their platforms."
